This project creates the ota package for the Artik 520/710 for Lwm2m update

Pre-requisites:-
1) Directory packages - Put all your rpm packages in this folder
2) packages.json - JSON manifest of the following format:
{
    "application" : "<application name>",
    "version" : "<version of the application>",
    "updatefirst" : <true if 'dnf update' should be run prior to installing the package, flase otherwise>,
    "options" : "<dnf options, only --allowerasing, --nogpgcheck and --best are supported>",
    "local_dependencies" : [
        {
            "name" : "<filename of the RPM to install>",
            "operation" : "<optional: dnf operation, only install, reinstall and downgrade are supported, by default: install>"
        }
    ],
    "packages" :
    [
        {
            "local_dependencies" : [
                {
                    "name" : "<filename of the RPM to install>",
                    "operation" : "optional: dnf operation, only install, reinstall and downgrade are supported, by default: inherit from package"
                }
            ],
            "name" : "<filename or pkg_spec of the RPM to install>",
            "operation" : "<optional: dnf operation, only install, reinstall and downgrade are supported, by default: install>"
        },
    ]

}


Build:-
make archive
